#. <section class="sutta" id="sn48.52"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn48.52:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 48"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 48"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn48.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Sūkarakhatavagga"
msgstr "6. The Boar’s Cave"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 52. Mallikasutta → mallakasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn48.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Mallikasutta"
msgstr "52. In the Land of the Mallas"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.52:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. VAR: mallesu → mallakesu (bj, s1-3, km) | mallikesu (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn48.52:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā mallesu viharati uruvelakappaṃ nāma mallānaṃ nigamo."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Mallas, near the "
"Mallian town called Uruvelakappa."

msgctxt "sn48.52:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn48.52:1.4"
msgid ""
"“yāvakīvañca, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa ariyañāṇaṃ na uppannaṃ hoti neva "
"tāva catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ saṇṭhiti hoti, neva tāva catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ "
"avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, as long as noble knowledge hasn’t arisen for a noble disciple "
"the four faculties are not stable and fixed."

msgctxt "sn48.52:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa ariyañāṇaṃ uppannaṃ hoti, atha "
"catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ saṇṭhiti hoti, atha catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"But when noble knowledge has arisen for a noble disciple the four faculties "
"become stable and fixed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.52:2.1"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yāvakīvañca kūṭāgārassa kūṭaṃ na ussitaṃ hoti, neva "
"tāva gopānasīnaṃ saṇṭhiti hoti, neva tāva gopānasīnaṃ avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s just like in a bungalow. As long as the roof peak is not lifted into "
"place, the rafters are not stable or fixed."

msgctxt "sn48.52:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa kūṭaṃ ussitaṃ hoti, atha gopānasīnaṃ "
"saṇṭhiti hoti, atha gopānasīnaṃ avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"But when the roof peak is lifted into place, the rafters become stable and "
"fixed."

msgctxt "sn48.52:2.3"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhikkhave, yāvakīvañca ariyasāvakassa ariyañāṇaṃ na uppannaṃ "
"hoti, neva tāva catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ saṇṭhiti hoti, neva tāva catunnaṃ "
"indriyānaṃ avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, as long as noble knowledge hasn’t arisen for a noble "
"disciple the four faculties are not stable and fixed."

msgctxt "sn48.52:2.4"
msgid ""
"Yato ca kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa ariyañāṇaṃ uppannaṃ hoti, atha "
"catunnaṃ indriyānaṃ … pe … avaṭṭhiti hoti."
msgstr ""
"But when noble knowledge has arisen for a noble disciple the four faculties "
"become stable and fixed."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.229"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn48.52:3.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn48.52:3.2"
msgid "Saddhindriyassa, vīriyindriyassa, satindriyassa, samādhindriyassa."
msgstr "The faculties of faith, energy, mindfulness, and immersion."

msgctxt "sn48.52:3.3"
msgid ""
"Paññavato, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa tadanvayā saddhā saṇṭhāti, tadanvayaṃ "
"vīriyaṃ saṇṭhāti, tadanvayā sati saṇṭhāti, tadanvayo samādhi saṇṭhātī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When a noble disciple has wisdom, the faith, energy, mindfulness, and "
"immersion that follow along with that become stabilized.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn48.52:3.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
